{"tid":931678,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豐澤事件唔等於惠康百佳價錯錢","createTime":"2018-12-07T08:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T13:31:30.000Z","uid":156902,"like":7,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1c94f4cee290640fc23c71208bd1bb6c35e636","tid":931678,"uid":156902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:01:17.000Z","msg":"★ Invitation to treat :<br />\nA邀請B提出要約﹙Offer﹚， B於是提出要約﹙Offer﹚給A， 而A之後表示接受﹙Acceptance﹚， 才構成合約Contract。<br />\n \t \t例一： 超級市場將標明價錢的貨品放在貨架上，只構成邀約，顧 客認為滿 意，拿到收銀員柜檯上，才構成顧客向超級市場作出要 約(OFFER)， 收銀員有權拒絕接受要約(例如因價錢有誤)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題在於豐澤有冇收到客人錢，有先有acceptance，再構成contract。<br />\n人地百佳惠康價錯錢，收返你錯嘅銀碼係因為唔想煩，唔係等如你啱！<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂咁搬出黎比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d639d0e001d56d80c26bd9b9fa4e6bd20704b0d2","tid":931678,"uid":97358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"係咪溫緊B Law<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad12913b9bac753012e2a34fda5384209786c9c","tid":931678,"uid":156902,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d639d0e001d56d80c26bd9b9fa4e6bd20704b0d2","tid":931678,"uid":97358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"係咪溫緊B Law<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"兩年前考完"},{"pid":"83a8c70cb9b3b0fa5790e4d4af5697d42a316fc0","tid":931678,"uid":106426,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd3d5552b418ad2ebe39a8f53a66c86dba998ebb","tid":931678,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:05:45.000Z","msg":"咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恥笑下班乞衣咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/d